cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper presents a method for automatic segmentation of MR images using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on medical imaging and bone quality assessment may also place the paper under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of deep learning techniques for segmentation may also suggest a connection to neural engineering (cs.NE).
